Epic. Arcade. Spaceflight. Action.

A spacefighter for the new age. Master your piloting prowess, take down swarms of starfighters, merciless armadas and colossal behemoths in an epic roguelike campaign that spans the stars and vanquish a malevolent evil that threatens to annihilate the cosmos.
